Description:
Functional Family Home in Meridian Estate
Positioned in Dandenongs newest and highly sought after Meridian Estate, this practical and ready to move into home is ideal for first home buyers, small families or investors looking to benefit from a solid rental return and expected capital growth. Offering all of the benefits of a modern and new home, the 8 year old property makes living easy with a functional and open planned living, meals and kitchen area, 3 bedrooms including master bedroom with full en suite and oversized walk in robe with inbuilt shelves and hangers, central family bathroom and single lock up garage with remote access and directly internal entry into the home. Additionally the home boasts an array of features including central gas ducted heating, low maintenance tiles through all living spaces and carpets in bedrooms, downlights in living area, outdoor decked verandah with weather protecting blinds and low maintenance gardens all round including artificial/synthetic grass. With a current rental income of $1912 per calendar month this property makes a smart long term investment. Arrange to inspect before it is gone!

Description:
BE DAZZLED BY THE IMMACULATE INTERIORS AND BRAND NEW CHARM!
An incredible opportunity for buyers on the hunt for a brand new townhouse that exudes contemporary class and dazzles with stylish fittings and fixtures, this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom residence with excellent street frontage could be your perfect match!
One of only two properties on the block and with no Body Corporate fees to pay, this sleek and light-filled home has first home buyers, young professionals, and small families in mind. Gleaming oversized floor tiles will impress straight away, as will the bright and spacious lounge and sizeable dining area. This dining space sits right next to the stone kitchen which is complete with stainless steel Westinghouse appliances.
A light-filled downstairs bedroom has access to a semi-ensuite which is splashed with striking floor-to-ceiling wall tiles. Two more bedrooms upstairs boast built-in robe storage including one of the bedrooms which has access to yet another chic semi-ensuite. Upstairs also have a versatile living space with plenty of room for both a retreat and study area, while a small balcony can be accessed off this zone.
Other features include a courtyard and easy garden, laundry, ducted heating and cooling, LED lighting, secure alarm, camera security, ducted vacuum, rainwater tank, and a double remote garage. Moments to Dandenong West Primary School, Dandenong High School, Gardiner Reserve, Hemmings Park, Fotheringham Nature Reserve, Dandenong Plaza Shopping Centre, buses, Yarraman Station, and Eastlink.

Contemporary Townhouse Living
Here's your chance to own a stylish two bedroom Townhouse/Unit in Dandenong's Metro Village Estate, built by renowned 'Burbank', one of Victoria's largest quality home builders.
Providing an open plan living/dining/kitchen area, two good sized bedrooms, courtyard, and remote garage it has everything you need.
Who needs a car when you're in this conveniently central location in Dandenong, considered Metropolitan Melbourne's second city centre, approximately 33km to Melbourne's CBD. A short stroll to the train station, tranquil parks, Dandenong plaza, bus stops, cafes & easy access to freeways.

• Neutral tonings, tiled living areas and carpeted bedrooms.
